title: [Upper Trollfang]
description: Your eyes strain to adjust to the varying intensities of light as you pass from deep shadow into brilliant shafts of golden sunlight.  The rapid changes make the darkness seem even more oppressive while the sunlight nearly blinds you.

Your eyes strain to adjust to the varying intensities of darkness as you pass from deep shadow into shafts of bright moonlight.  The rapid changes make the darkness seem even more oppressive while the moonlight relaxes you.
